namacut (2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major UI redesign with modern dark theme and panel-based layout.
  * Implemented drag-and-drop functionality for video files.
  * Added video rotation, flip, and crop features with live preview.
  * Introduced advanced export settings dialog for format, quality, and bitrate.
  * Added millisecond precision for accurate time selection.
  * Implemented progress bar with percentage display.
  * Added post-export actions (show message, open folder, close app).
  * Improved overall stability and error handling.

 -- Pourdaryaei <pourdaryaei@yandex.com>  Tue, 18 Nov 2025 20:00:00 +0330

